{"type": "article", "id": 32424, "title": "LOEWE新CEO来自Céline，以及，陈奕迅也出了首个联名款 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-09-21T02:32:31Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 162, "name": "米兰"}, {"id": 2944, "name": "伦敦时装周"}, {"id": 3865, "name": "adidas Originals"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 1110, "name": "喜达屋"}, {"id": 2882, "name": "Tory Burch"}, {"id": 3263, "name": "Loewe"}, {"id": 3350, "name": "Louis Vuitton"}, {"id": 4289, "name": "万豪"}, {"id": 6654, "name": "Etsy"}, {"id": 32984, "name": "Melissa"}, {"id": 976, "name": "Rihanna"}, {"id": 5844, "name": "陈奕迅"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160921092935lUoJLAzkRSa7bjiq.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/us-starwood-hotels-m-a-marriott-intnl-idUSKCN11Q1OW\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>中国商务部批准万豪收购喜达屋</b></a> | 今年 3 月万豪以 136 亿美元的报价成功收购喜达屋。此前万豪和喜达屋已经获得了超过 40 个国家监管机构的批准，包括美国、欧盟、加拿大和日本，中国是并购案需要通过的最后一个国家。&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, Helvetica, Tahoma, 'Arial sans-serif'; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/business-features/tory-burch-seeks-applicants-annual-fellows-program-10555528/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Tory Burch 基金会在进行新一轮的申请</b></a> | Tory Burch 基金会于 2015 年成立，旨在为女性创业提供帮助。该项目的奖金包括 1 万美元的商业教育基金，Tory Burch 总部的免费参观旅行，以及参与奖金为 10 万美元的创业比赛的名额。去年，有超过 500 位申请者，赞助了其中 10 位女性创业家。</span></p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/etsy-acquires-blackbird-technologies-brand-campaign-10556056/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国手工工艺品电商 Etsy 收购 Blackbird 科技</b></a> | 据 Etsy 称，此次收购 Blackbird 科技，是希望借由 Blackbird 的后端技术来帮助 Etsy 网站创造更好的购物体验。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://www.vogue.co.uk/article/loewe-new-ceo-pascale-lepoivre-celine\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>LOEWE 任命新的 CEO </b></a>| Pascale Lepoivre 将成为 LOEWE 的新一任首席执行官，他曾经是  Céline 的 CEO。此次将加入 LOEWE，与创意总监 Jonathan Anderson 一起工作。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/designer-luxury/gucci-milan-headquarters-10555707/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Gucci 新的米兰总部揭幕</b></a> | Gucci 在米兰的新总部位于 Via Mecenate 的一座始建于 1915 年的工厂，该工厂占地 378000 平方英尺，约 35117 平方米，Gucci 的米兰总部办公室以及秀场都在这里。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921101354koAIhzM4WRQcH0BP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/louis-vuitton-2016-fw-sense-editorial\" rel=\"nofollow\">Louis Vuitton 联手日本时尚杂志《SENSE》打造 2016 秋冬季造型特辑</a>，军事风格单品融入暗黑背景，呈现神秘氛围。该系列包括长风衣、bomber 夹克等大热单品，以及丝绸衬衫等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921092007tLBl9zsqYgDKxnfy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921092007gh5WciC6J1uyPRmV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921092007dcgmUV8S1RrhKGju.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921092007dPQ43zSsmUwoIGDa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921092008iNPrWI8uQnt5ehcF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921092008eThEpuQtL6mU7vj1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921092019mFeghpnZDbdM3oBz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>在伦敦时装周上，以果冻鞋出名的巴西品牌 Melissa，与 The Cambridge Satchel Company 合作，推出一系列<a href=\"http://popbee.com/accessories/handbags/melissa-x-cambridge-satchel-collaboration/\" rel=\"nofollow\">限量包款</a>。包括红色、黑色以及最惹眼的幻彩色。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921092033oBqfIED1nveR0r2F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921092033Zg5HxGpALtySNlTY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609210920475QWFIxhgv9d731oU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609210920475XKarTgU1tSCbIn3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921092047C32geHm1JuqpPWUt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">来看<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/streetsnaps-london-fashion-week-september-2016-part-2\" rel=\"nofollow\"> 2017 春夏伦敦时装周街拍特辑</a>。Vetements、Thrasher、VLONE、PACCBET 热门单品悉数亮相。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609210920585flNsjDBALUFJPz1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921092059TyzdOWoXFlPVRC6n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921092059kLgjXVA9JCeDHPYh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921092059Xq1Lo5uGOsRpKbmx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921092109GV6ebmOCB2xwFL15.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921092109lLhyVYm1xTo2NAbM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921092109NvibmwTIeDogxq3M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921092109FqgNreDmzuM2pVyX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921092109LV835qyZeQ6HJAUv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921092110B6UOWLfMJXdZ2Swt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/rihanna-cr-fashion-book-2016-photos/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Rihanna 登上美国女性时尚生活摄影杂志 CR FASHION BOOK </a>的第九期封面。该杂志是《Vogue》前法国版主编  Carine Roitfeld ，离开《Vogue》杂志后创办的，一年仅出刊两次。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921092124AwNIh4vZkb2zB90O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921092124l76EsOd5UBJyAL4M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334635\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921092124ygWwKUEHPFYmRAtv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.339844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609210921362nJidoT1wOhHjZ57.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.335938\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921092143UtTlW7cKY5zLjCqD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332031\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">adidas Originals 与陈奕迅合作，推出全新 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/adidas-originals-x-eason-chan-first-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">adidas Originals x Eason Chan </a>系列。这也是 Eason 第一次担任设计师亲自设计，从简约的风格出发，以灰色、蓝色、黑色为基调，带来了卫衣、T-shirt、连帽外套、长裤等一系列单品。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609210922009U3mRYg6CzPXLs0r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921092159yL8kU1rzbsxmavGq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921092200TW5oqUt91NFcCenH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921092200JBwaYzEjDGxX413y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609210922150mYQvaNkdM9jFsqy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921092215sdz5v4mwkL8PWMqZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921092224ko4P6VTvQpAHeij9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}